# Copy to .env.local for local development. NEVER commit a real key — .gitignore blocks it.
#
# Used only by the serverless function (api/analyze-meal.ts), server-side.
# It is never bundled into the client and never sent to the browser.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com  →  API Keys
# In production, set this in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# When this is unset, the app still works fully — the AI scan feature disables itself
# and returns 503 { "error": "ai_unconfigured" }. Nothing breaks.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
